  h1 Accomodation

  p There aren't a lot of hotels really close by. There are however plenty of B&B's so for people coming by car there are more choices.

  h2 Dale Hill Hotel and Golf Club

  p This hotel is close to the church and dinner. We have reserved a number of rooms that are available for wedding guests.

  p We've managed to reserve the following rooms at slighly better than stock prices. First to sign up applies.

  ul
    li 3 double rooms, 110 GBP/night
    li 3 twin bed rooms, 110 GBP/night
    li 2 small double rooms, 110 GBP/night
    li 2 double rooms with golf course view, 130 GBP/night
    li 1 twin bed room with golf course view, 130 GBP/night

  p Prices include breakfast. Extra beds for kids can be arranged.

  p I think you can book rooms also outside of those 10 rooms, but I'm not sure about prices.

  p If you have trouble finding accomodation please get in touch and we'll try to find more alternatives.

