  h2 Bed and Breakfasts

  p There are plenty of B&B's in the area of all price ranges and standards. This is a list of nearby alternatives: #{{link_to('Cranbrook B&Bs', 'http://www.cranbrook.org/accommodation.php')}}. In general Google is your friend and there are several websites liks this one available to assist: #{{link_to('http://www.britainsfinest.co.uk/bedandbreakfast', 'http://www.britainsfinest.co.uk/bedandbreakfast')}}

  h2 Tunbridge Wells

  p The closest town is Tunbridge Wells, about 25-30min away by car.

  p Tunbridge Wells has several hotels, but having had a look around we'd recommend B&B's as a better alternative. It is however available if you have a hard time finding a room.

